trans-unit.source: Represents the messages to be broken up into their logical units with specific abstract information for each part.
trans-unit.target: 表示要分解成其包含的特定抽象信息的每个部分的逻辑单元的消息。

trans-unit.source: The MessagePart class corresponds to a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) `part` element enclosed by the `message` element, which is in turn enclosed by the `definitions` root element.
trans-unit.target: 消息部分类对应到 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL)`part`括在元素`message`元素，它又被括`definitions`根元素。

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 有关 WSDL 的详细信息，请参阅 http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/ 的规范。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the name of the XML element that corresponds to the current <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置相对应的 XML 元素的名称与当前<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `element` attribute of the `part` element for which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> class serves as a wrapper.
trans-unit.target: 此属性对应于`element`属性`part`元素为其<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>类用作包装器。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>

trans-unit.source: The name of the XML element that corresponds to the current <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 对应于当前的 XML 元素名称<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Message"></xref> of which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> is a member.
The message of which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> is a member.
Gets or sets the XML data type of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置的 XML 数据类型<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: This property corresponds to the `type` attribute of the `part` element for which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> class serves as a wrapper.
trans-unit.target: 此属性对应于`type`属性`part`元素为其<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>类用作包装器。</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>

trans-unit.source: In general, it refers to a data type defined in the XSD schema, but it can also be extended, as long as the XML namespace used is different from that of Web Services Description Language (WSDL).
trans-unit.target: 一般情况下，它引用 XSD 架构中定义的数据类型，但它还可以进行扩展，只要使用的 XML 命名空间不同于 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL)。
